                        <h4 class="itemtitle">
                            <a href="http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/tkMJiR_FunM/">Land Rover Defender V8   推 007 限量版全球僅 300 部</a>
                        </h4>
                        <h5 class="itemposttime">
                            <span>Posted:</span>Tue, 07 Sep 2021 23:01:18 +0000
                        </h5>
                        <div class="itemcontent" name="decodeable"><p>因為疫情緣故上映多番延期的 007 電影《No Time to Die》，如無意外將會在 9 月底全球推出。作為電影的合作夥伴，Land Rover 日前發表了由旗下 SV Bespoke 部門特別定制的 Defender V8 Bond Edition 電影特別版，有短軸 90 和長軸 110 兩個版本，全球限量推出 300 部。</p><p><span id="more-1058272"></span></p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/07/land-rover-defender-v8-bond-edition/movie-2/attachment/0906-1a-8/" rel="attachment wp-att-1058293"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1058293" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0906-1a-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0906-1a-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0906-1a-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0906-1a-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0906-1a-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0906-1a.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在最新 007 電影《No Time to Die》中，Land Rover Defender、Range Rover Sport SVR、Range Rover Classic 和 Land Rover Series III 都會現身。採用全黑色車身塗裝的 Defender V8 Bond Edition，搭配黑色 Extended Black Pack 套件和 22 吋亮黑色 Gloss Black 輪圈，整部車低調有型。前輪的煞車卡鉗用上藍色 Xenon Blue 烤漆點綴，而車尾行李箱有 007 專屬標誌裝飾，突顯限量版的矜貴。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_13128"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332"  src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DstNptnfN7g?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>Defender V8 Bond Edition 的內裝，儀表台外側和車門之間有 SV Bespoke 圖案和限量版銘牌，而資訊娛樂系統的觸控屏幕亦有 007 專屬開機畫面。門檻金屬踏板和投射到地面的迎賓燈都有 007 標誌。顧名思義 Defender V8 Bond Edition 配備 5.0L V8 機械增壓引擎，能夠輸出 525 匹馬力和 625Nm 峰值扭力，搭配 8 速自動波箱和 Land Rover 引以為傲的四驅系統。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.motortrend.com/news/land-rover-defender-v-8-bond-edition/">motortrend</a></p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/08/land-rover-defender-v8-bond-edition/movie-2/">Land Rover Defender V8   推 007 限量版全球僅 300 部</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk">香港 unwire.hk 玩生活．樂科技</a>.</p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=tkMJiR_FunM:DojRjjErgu8:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=tkMJiR_FunM:DojRjjErgu8:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/tkMJiR_FunM" height="1" width="1" alt=""/></div>
