                        <h4 class="itemtitle">
                            <a href="http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/GEYcY3zGoR8/">Mercedes-Benz EQE 發佈   外形大變身 + 660 公里續航力</a>
                        </h4>
                        <h5 class="itemposttime">
                            <span>Posted:</span>Tue, 07 Sep 2021 10:18:19 +0000
                        </h5>
                        <div class="itemcontent" name="decodeable"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Mercedes-Benz 近日一次過發佈四款電動車，當中最矚目的莫過於全新登場的量產純電動行政房車 EQE。EQE 實際上可看作是純電版的 E-Class Sedan。資料顯示，Mercedes-Benz EQE 的續航力達 660 公里。，總長度為 4,934mm，軸距達 3,120mm。外型有如短小版的 EQS，外觀採用比傳統 E-Class 更近似轎跑車的設計。而車頭的密閉式鬼面罩由 Mercedes-Benz 顯眼的標誌以及佈滿星形圖案的黑色底板所組成，而尾部則與同系 EQ 車款設計相若。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058527 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163098849199823_P13738310-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163098849199823_P13738310-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163098849199823_P13738310-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163098849199823_P13738310.jpg 1049w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058525 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163097509078843_P13738219-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163097509078843_P13738219-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163097509078843_P13738219-768x429.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163097509078843_P13738219.jpg 1048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058528 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163099321254238_P13738235-694x420.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="420" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163099321254238_P13738235-694x420.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163099321254238_P13738235-768x465.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163099321254238_P13738235.jpg 1049w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058530 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163100393531043_P13738243-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163100393531043_P13738243-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163100393531043_P13738243-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163100393531043_P13738243.jpg 1049w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058532 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163093998912872_P13738225-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163093998912872_P13738225-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163093998912872_P13738225-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163093998912872_P13738225.jpg 1049w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">EQE350車型配備 90.6 kWh 鋰電池組搭配 215kW 電動馬達，擁有最大 288hp 馬力與 54kg-m 的扭力輸出。而車身內亦配備一體式的 MBUX Hyperscreen，由 12.3 吋虛擬儀表版、17.7 吋OLED中控螢幕以及 12.3 吋 OLED 副駕駛座螢幕組成。電池續航力在 WLTP 循環測試中，EQE 的續航里程可達 660 公里，可在 31 分鐘內能將電池從 10% 充到 80%。EQE 在電動動力系統 (eATS) 的設計也考慮了噪音和行車震動的舒適性。 </span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058534 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163100393584704_P13738227-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163100393584704_P13738227-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163100393584704_P13738227-768x422.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/163100393584704_P13738227.jpg 1048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058535 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-1-694x392.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-1-694x392.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-1-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-1.jpg 1049w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058536 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-2-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-2-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-2.jpg 1049w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058537 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-3-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-3-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/photo-3.jpg 1049w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">EQE 的懸吊系統採用前四連桿，後多連桿的設定。而選配的後輪轉向系統可提供高達 10° 的轉向角。同時更可選配帶有 ADS + 主動調整阻尼的 AIRMATIC 氣壓懸吊系統。此外，EQE 同時設有另一 Performance 動力版本，不過原廠尚未公布，粗略估計其動力將會比現有的更加強大，預計達到 670 匹馬力的水平。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>資料來源：Mercedes-Benz</p><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/07/mercedes-benz-eqe/life-tech/auto/">Mercedes-Benz EQE 發佈   外形大變身 + 660 公里續航力</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk">香港 unwire.hk 玩生活．樂科技</a>.</p><div class="feedflare">
